"La Marsottière" is a diversified farm in AB of course and since September 2019 under the label Nature & Progrès, where we carry out authentic and respectful agricultural productions in :
. Strawberries and small red fruits (raspberries, blackcurrants, redcurrants and even blueberries!) ;
. Raw milk and dairy products from our Jersey cows (dairy processing laboratory) and rearing their calves ;
. A conservatory orchard (established in 2018) with insect hotels and a few beehives ;
. Vegetable (with market gardening) and fruit processing;
. A cultural itinerary in accordance with the soil and our "ecological" engines: Thank you donkeys!
Rural reception on the farm (wwoofing,, farmer's welcome, guest rooms & tables) ;
